author: @jolbrias1
content:
It’s truly amazing but NOT surprising that this concert in Rio de Janeiro made history for Madonna with The Celebration Tour with over 1.6 million people, which became Madonna's largest crowd of her career and set records for the largest audience ever for a stand-alone concert and the largest all-time crowd for a female artist.

I saw her on January 9, 2024 in Boston MA & there were 19,580 people there & I couldn’t imagine being in a crowd of over 1.6 Million people. I love the energy & how it’s such a HUGE party.
